# Getting all the values of all the contracts in the tree

If we use TreeDumper, which inherits ITreeVisitor interface, we are able to get the dump of all the accounts and values of the State Tree.

For example, for [this contract](https://github.com/xdaichain/intern-beacon-chain/blob/main/smart_contracts/toGetData.sol) we will get:
